            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Flavio Camill<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>IIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Hel</abbr><ex>vetiorum</ex></expan> flamini <lb n="3"/>Augusti <lb n="4"/>quem ordo patronum <lb n="5"/>civitatis cooptavit <expan><abbr>eiq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>ob merita eius erga rem <lb n="7"/>publicam scholam et <lb n="8"/>statuas decrevit <lb n="9"/>vikani <lb n="10"/>Eburodunenses <lb n="11"/>amico et patrono
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Blattförmige hedera als Worttrenner in Z. 7 u. 8. Unterhalb der Inschrift zwei Palmzweige.</p>
            </div>
